block content
    //- include ../layouts/banner.pug
    main.academics-page.container-lg

        h3.academics-page__introduction Explore the dynamic campus of Iqbal Institute of Technology and Management (IITM) Srinagar, where academic excellence harmonizes with a vibrant student life. Our canteen offers a diverse menu, ensuring quality, hygiene, and affordability. While our hostels are in progress, we collaborate with a third party to provide affordable living spaces. Embrace holistic development through our state-of-the-art sports facilities and diverse activities. Our transportation service, with two buses and multiple pickup locations, ensures a convenient commute for all. Discover a comprehensive and enriching college experience at IITM, where every aspect of student life is thoughtfully considered.

        div.margin-top-sm.margin-bottom-md
            .square-cards
                .square-cards__item 
                    a(href="/campus/canteen")
                        img(src="/data/imgs/canteen-banner.jpg")
                        div
                            h2 Canteen
                            p Culinary diversity, quality, and affordability.

                .square-cards__item 
                    a(href="/campus/hostel")
                        img(src="/data/imgs/hostel-banner.jpg")
                        div
                            h2 Hostel
                            p Culinary diversity, quality, and affordability.

                .square-cards__item 
                    a(href="/campus/sports")
                        img(src="/data/collegeImgs/sports.JPG")
                        div
                            h2 Sports
                            p Holistic development through state-of-the-art facilities.

                .square-cards__item 
                    a(href="/campus/transportation")
                        img(src="/data/imgs/transportation-banner.jpg")
                        div
                            h2 Transportation
                            p Convenient commute with multiple pickup locations.